<section>
  <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  <div class="faq-list">
    
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Q: What is Team Rocket's Warehouse?</h3>
      <p>A: Team Rocket's Warehouse is your go-to place for trading, collecting, and battling Pokémon cards! It’s like Giovanni’s secret base, but with more trading and fewer plans for world domination.</p>
      <img src="/images/onix.gif" alt="Onix GIF" class="faq-gif">
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Q: How do I trade Pokémon cards?</h3>
      <p>A: Trading cards is as easy as throwing a Poké Ball! Just visit the trade section, select the cards you want to trade, and make your offer. It’s like a Pokémon battle, but with less dodging and more bargaining.</p>
      <img src="/images/pikachu.gif" alt="Pikachu GIF" class="faq-gif">
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Q: Can I battle other trainers?</h3>
      <p>A: Absolutely! Take your best Pokémon cards into battle and prove you’re the best like no one ever was. Just make sure your cards are in top condition, like a freshly healed Pokémon at the Poké Center!</p>
      <img src="/images/charizard.gif" alt="Charizard GIF" class="faq-gif">
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Q: What happens if my trade offer is rejected?</h3>
      <p>A: Don’t worry! Just like catching Pokémon, sometimes it takes more than one try. Adjust your offer and try again – you’ll catch that perfect trade eventually!</p>
      <img src="/images/snorlax.gif" alt="Snorlax GIF" class="faq-gif">
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Q: How do I manage my collection?</h3>
      <p>A: You can manage your collection by going to your profile page. It’s like organizing your Pokémon party – make sure your best cards are always ready for battle!</p>
      <img src="/images/mewtwo.gif" alt="Mewtwo GIF" class="faq-gif">
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

